{"tid":430170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角騷亂案　法官拒開槍警員出庭作供","createTime":"2017-10-09T14:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T14:31:15.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"36a78a21072e6c2d774267e3f4faac996834cb37","tid":430170,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T14:31:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">旺角騷亂案　法官拒開槍警員出庭作供</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】旺角騷亂案，其中一名被告要求傳召當晚向天開槍的警員出庭作供，被法官拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n第七被告鄧敬宗一方要求傳召當晚向天開槍的交通警員出庭作供，認為警員是非法開槍，被告的行為只是自衛，控方反對，指無任何證供顯示被告擔心自己的安全。<br />\n<br />\n法官接納控方的說法，認為警員的證供與本案不相關，因此拒絕傳召該名警員，案件押後至本月19日結案陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=238763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D238763&d=1sL3qW5UPY4I6ATSgvDB5QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8cebb32d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D238763&h=93b0c177\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=238763</a>"}]}